      <title>特斯拉将重回凯西·伍德旗舰基金的榜首位置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tesla-set-to-recover-top-spot-in-cathie-wood-s-flagship-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着凯西·伍德 (Cathie Wood) 的公司买入这家电动汽车制造商股价的下跌，特斯拉公司有望恢复其在凯西·伍德 (Cathie Wood) 主要基金中的最高地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tesla-set-to-recover-top-spot-in-cathie-wood-s-flagship-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能热潮让台积电领衔的台湾股市领先韩国股市更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tsmc-drives-taiwanese-equities-to-outperform-tech-rival-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾股市已经击败了科技竞争对手韩国，因为这两个市场都在争夺全球一些最大的基金管理公司的人工智能投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tsmc-drives-taiwanese-equities-to-outperform-tech-rival-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 04:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
